<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">High on the list of crypto=E2=80=99s most impr=
essive accomplishments is the ability of crypto finance to convince people =
to=C2=A0<em>lend money</em>, at very high loan-to-value ratios, against col=
lateral that is somewhere between =E2=80=9Cextremely risky=E2=80=9D and =E2=
=80=9Ctransparently worthless.=E2=80=9D We have <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnL=
mNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTEtMTQvZnR4LXMtYmFsYW5jZS1zaGVldC13YXMt=
YmFkP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAyMTQyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJ=
jZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDIxNCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607=
f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBc6fb60c7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemsco=
pe" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> repeatedly about the t=
ime Sam Bankman-Fried said to me,=C2=A0on a podcast, that in crypto you can=
 build a box and issue tokens from the box and =E2=80=9Cput [the] token in =
a borrow lending protocol and borrow dollars with it=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9C=
never, you know, give the dollars back.=E2=80=9D And we have talked about h=
ow Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s FTX crypto exchange did more or less exactly tha=
t, borrowing billions of dollars of customer money against its stash of mad=
e-up tokens and not giving the money back.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And we have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9v=
cGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTItMDUvY3J5cHRvLWhhZC1hLWNyZWRpdC1idWJibGU_Y21=
waWQ9QkJEMDIxNDIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3=
NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwMjE0JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b=
8524a319a23cB35bddd22" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targe=
t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked=C2=A0about</a> Kyle Davies, one of =
the founders of crypto trading firm Three Arrows Capital, or 3AC, whose sup=
erpower was convincing people to lend him hundreds of millions of dollars t=
o do crypto =E2=80=9Carbitrage=E2=80=9D trades that were just, like, buying=
 speculative tokens of new crypto protocols, holding them for a while and h=
oping they=E2=80=99d go up. The innovations in 3AC=E2=80=99s business model=
 were:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Calling=C2=A0wildly risky venture-typ=
e=C2=A0investments=C2=A0=E2=80=9Carbitrages,=E2=80=9D so that lenders would=
 assume they were safe, and</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Findin=
g some really gullible lenders.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As Davies <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2=
g_dj1Uekdka0IweGJDRSZ0PTFz/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB88afcb4a" itemprop=3D"S=
toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> said=
 in an interview</a>: =E2=80=9CI think one of the last calls we did someone=
 lent me high nine figures, almost a billion, off a phone call. That was th=
e final one, that was, like, uncollateralized. That=E2=80=99s where the sys=
tem was. People needed to get dollars out the door.=E2=80=9D He could help =
them with that problem. The dollars did not come back=C2=A0<em>in=C2=A0</em=
>the door; 3AC is now bankrupt, and Davies and his cofounder Su Zhu are all=
egedly=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/305525=
42.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmFzZGFxLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy90aHJlZS1hcnJvd3MtY2Fwa=
XRhbC1zYXlzLWl0cy1mb3VuZGVycy1zdGlsbC1ub3QtY29vcGVyYXRpbmctd2l0aC1hc3NldC1y=
ZWNvdmVyeQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBe8757ed6" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemsc=
ope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoratio=
n: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000;=
 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">not helping its liqui=
dators</a> find whatever money is left.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Based on past results I guess I would say that=
 3AC=E2=80=99s founders are maybe not that great at=C2=A0<em>trading</em>, =
but they are world-historically good at getting people to lend money agains=
t nonsense, and in crypto in the early 2020s that was a=C2=A0valuable skill=
. They=E2=80=99re <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy90aHJlZS1hcnJvd3MtZm9=
1bmRlcnMtc3RhcnQtY3J5cHRvLWJhbmtydXB0Y3ktY2xhaW1zLWV4Y2hhbmdlLWYwNzQ3MjhmP2=
1vZD1pdHBfd3NqJnJ1PXlhaG9v/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB9efe4d85" itemprop=3D"S=
toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> gonn=
a try it again</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The founders of failed hedge fund Three Arrows=
 Capital Ltd. have resurfaced with a $25 million crypto-exchange venture th=
at will let users trade bankruptcy claims from insolvent platforms and fund=
s, including their own.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Open Exchange, or OPNX, was created by Su Zhu =
and Kyle Davies=E2=80=94who set up Three Arrows together=E2=80=94and the tw=
o founders of crypto exchange CoinFLEX. The new platform is expected to lau=
nch by the end of this month, Mr. Zhu said. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The company=E2=80=99s website said there is a =
$20 billion market of crypto claimants, and the exchange will allow credito=
rs to convert their claims into cryptocurrencies to use them as margin coll=
ateral for crypto futures trading. Claims against Three Arrows Capital are =
among those that can be traded on the new exchange, in addition to claims a=
gainst FTX, Genesis Global Capital, Celsius Network LLC and others, OPNX sa=
id.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CUse them as margin collateral for cry=
pto futures trading=E2=80=9D! We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGl=
uaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDEtMTcvc2VjLWNvbWVzLWZvci1nZW1pbmktdG9vLWxhdGU_Y2=
1waWQ9QkJEMDIxNDIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld=
