rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">  discussed this plan before</a>, and I lov=
e it. Like:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">3AC borrows a lot of money to buy tok=
ens, posting the tokens as collateral for the loans.</li>=09<li style=3D"ma=
rgin-bottom: 5px;">The tokens turn out to be worthless, 3AC doesn=E2=80=99t=
 pay back the loans=C2=A0and goes bankrupt.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 5px;">3AC helps the lenders turn the loans into new tokens, listed on i=
ts own bankruptcy token exchange.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">=
Traders on the exchange borrow a lot of money to buy the new tokens, postin=
g the new tokens as collateral for the loans.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bo=
ttom: 5px;">If you were to write =E2=80=9Cgo to Step 2,=E2=80=9D who would =
blame you?</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It is so pure? We <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
NvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMTMvdGhlLXNlYy1jcmFja3MtZG93bi1vbi1jc=
