t=E2=80=99s weird to have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/30552542.269805/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYXBlcnMuc3Nybi5jb20vc29sMy9wYXBlcnMuY2Z=
